00:00:01.850 --> 00:00:03.910
JOE: Tonight's speaker
is Nataly Kelly.

00:00:03.910 --> 00:00:05.760
You may have heard of Nataly.

00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:08.720
She is Chief Research Officer
at Common Sense Advisory.

00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:12.230
She's been in the Language
Services industry since 1996.

00:00:12.230 --> 00:00:14.660
