Shapes Our Lives and

00:01:29.720 --> 00:01:31.410
Transforms the World."

00:01:31.410 --> 00:01:32.830
And it's not just a subtitle.

00:01:32.830 --> 00:01:34.280
This really means something.

00:01:34.280 --> 00:01:36.620
And I'm going to explain why
we chose that subtitle

00:01:36.620 --> 00:01:38.490
throughout my talk.

00:01:38.490 --> 00:01:41.780
So, a lot of people, when they
think of translation, think

00:01:41.780 --> 00:01:46.250
about academic exercises,
and think about literary

00:01:46.250 --> 00:01:47.330
translation.

00:01:47.330 --> 00:01:49.320
And if they think about
interpreting at all, they tend

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:50.900
to think about conference
interpreting.

00:01:50.900 --> 00:01:52.820
Now, how many of you
speak another

00:01:52.820 --> 00:01:55.410
