00:02:12.070 --> 00:02:13.050
[LAUGHS].

00:02:13.050 --> 00:02:13.630
Excellent.

00:02:13.630 --> 00:02:16.030
So we have a pretty multilingual
group here today.

00:02:16.030 --> 00:02:18.220
And how many of you have
